{"tid":713090,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【情深款款】殿堂級天后過於投入 不慎唱出「屌」字!!!","createTime":"2018-06-22T14:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T02:02:46.000Z","uid":24160,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2d5031efa1a593682e5ce94dec7aac7177a2d3a1","tid":713090,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:27:32.000Z","msg":"香港殿堂級Diva 再次穿上露肩服裝,<br />\n打扮成Tinker Bell 奇妙仙子, 為大家同中樂團獻唱<br />\n李清照所寫嘅 《聲慢慢》<br />\n一齊欣賞汪阿姐嘅歌喉啦~~~<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/O8MtVX-AggE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FO8MtVX-AggE&d=ehzDsiRqX84m4WCA67yTei7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=5ad56dcf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/O8MtVX-AggE</a><br />\n<br />\n⚠️注意:&quot;靚聲位&quot; (引號)<br />\n<br />\n最美麗亞洲真人版Tinker Bell 示意圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/212808_fdf8ab615823a6f09291d899ed0a9e14.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F212808_fdf8ab615823a6f09291d899ed0a9e14.png&h=c9aa3b0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4:20 到黃<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">昏&uarr;&uarr; [size=6][red]點&uarr;&uarr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><em>屌&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</em></strong></span></span>滴滴。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/J8WKeUr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJ8WKeUr.gif&h=61d50d20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋尋覓覓，冷冷清清，淒淒慘慘戚戚。乍暖還寒時候，最難將息。三盃兩盞淡酒，3:24怎敵他晚來<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">風&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</span></span>急！<br />\r\n3:31 雁過也，正傷心，卻是舊時<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;相~~~ng~~&rdquo;</span></span>識。(chok 咪)　<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/u3Vbv7x.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fu3Vbv7x.gif&h=32e630fd&s={SIZE}\" />　<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3:42 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;滿&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;~~~~~~&rdquo;地黃[size=6][red]花&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;~~~</span></span>堆積。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n3:51<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;憔&rdquo;</span></span>悴<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">損↗↘</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如&darr;&darr;&darr;↕↕↕↕</span></span>今有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">誰&darr;&darr;&darr;↕↕↕↕堪&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;摘&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;&uarr;&darr;？守&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;~~~&ldquo;wuwuwuwuu&rdquo;</span></span> 著<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">窗&uarr;&uarr;↗↘兒iiiii&ldquo;iar&rdquo;~~</span></span>，獨<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;自&rdquo;</span></span>怎<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">生&uarr;&uarr;得&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;黑&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;~~~~~~</span></span>。<br />\r\n<br />\n4:10(情深款款的樣子)<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&ldquo;梧&rdquo;</span></span>桐<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更&uarr;&uarr;&ldquo;兼&uarr;&uarr;&rdquo;</span></span>細雨，到黃<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">昏&uarr;&uarr; [size=6][red]點&uarr;&uarr;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">屌&uarr;&uarr;&uarr;</span></span>滴滴。這次第，怎一個愁字了<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">得~~~~~！ </span></span>"},{"pid":"8ad97a4a823b77053413bfcde3e025f37476e23b","tid":713090,"uid":24160,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:27:48.000Z","msg":"<strong><span